%% Epoch boundary: closeEpoch + fee-per-share (FR-13, INV-06)
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> EpochOpen: beforeInitialize / closeEpoch
    EpochOpen --> Accumulating: swaps (afterSwap)
    Accumulating --> Accumulating: epochSeniorFunded += senior slice
    Accumulating --> CloseReady: timestamp >= epochStart + smoothingEpochSeconds
    CloseReady --> Settling: closeEpoch()
    state Settling {
        [*] --> SurplusShortfall
        SurplusShortfall --> DrawReserve: shortfall > 0
        DrawReserve --> FundSenior: juniorReserve -= cover
        SurplusShortfall --> CreditShare: senior/junior feePerShareX128 +=
        CreditShare --> Reset: epoch++, fees=0, new obligation
    }
    Settling --> EpochOpen: epochStartTimestamp = now
